{"about_the_game":"<strong>Experience VR like never before. Without the headset!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collection of non-virtual, reality games!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> All games are played in the real world<br></li><li> All necessary information is conveyed through controller vibration and sound!<br></li><li> Play locally with your friends. Each using one controller<br></li><li> Wide variety of games</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How To Play</h2>Put your VR headset to the side, where its still visible to the trackers. Then turn up your volume, so you can hear the game.<br>Finally give each player one of the controllers. Now you are ready to go!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Games</h2>Select from a variety of party games! Contains a total of 5 games, all specifically designed for this type of interaction!<br>Most of these are played with or against a friend locally. Some can be played alone. <br><br>For example create your own universe in <strong>I Packed my Universe</strong>, a fresh take on the classic <i>I Packed my Suitcase</i> game. Place planets freely in your room and keep track of their positions. Because you can only add a new one after confirming the positions of each previously placed planet. <br><br>Or free your room of spooky creatures in <strong>Ghost Hunter</strong>! Use the virbations of the controllers to track their location and pull them apart!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Supported Hardware</h2>We are currently only supporting Valve Index and HTC Vive systems, as these have external base stations for tracking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Contact</h2>Have further questions or want to show our game at your event? Let's get in touch! <strong><a href=\"mailto:nonvr.games@gmail.com\">nonvr.games@gmail.com</a></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Background</h2>This project was created as part of the the Games Master study program at the HAW Hamburg University Of Applied Sciences.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2449320?t=17